title: Vasa Cylinder Sculpture
description:
Some years ago, Vasa created methods of sculpting with cast acrylic forms. Perfecting his technique over time, the artist has created a stunning, vibrant vocabulary all his own. Be sure to observe from every angle. Sculptor Vasa Velizar Mihich and his team create each piece by hand in Los Angeles CA. Signed by the artist.

  • Dimensions: 2.4 x 3.75 in.

*Please note that due to the handmade nature, each product may vary in design/look/appearance.
